            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve"><head>Text</head><div n="1" type="textpart"><ab><lb n="1"/>
                <expan><abbr>L</abbr><ex>ucio</ex></expan> Oppio |(mulieris) <expan><abbr>l</abbr><ex>iberto</ex></expan> Iamo <lb n="2"/>Oppiae Grapte <lb n="3"/>Albinovana <expan><abbr>C</abbr><ex>ai</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>l</abbr><ex>iberta</ex></expan> <lb n="4"/>Iame patri et matri <lb n="5"/><expan><abbr>posterisq</abbr><ex>ue</ex></expan> suis </ab></div><div n="2" type="textpart"><ab><lb n="1"/> in <expan><abbr>fr</abbr><ex>onte</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>p</abbr><ex>edes</ex></expan> XII </ab></div><div n="3" type="textpart"><ab><lb n="1"/> in <expan><abbr>agr</abbr><ex>o</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>p</abbr><ex>edes</ex></expan> XV
            </ab></div></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Tafel gehörte zur Sammlung Gorga. Maßangaben stehen in kleineren Buchstaben auf beiden Seiten von posterisque suis. Tochter hat anderes nomen gentile als Eltern. Z. 1: bei Pseudofiliation ursprünglich D eingemeißelt, dann nachträglich verbessert.</p>
            </div>
